00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:04,087
Pay special attention to the third line on the right column.

2
00:00:04,037 --> 00:00:10,137
The biggest difference with an agent isn't that it's smarter—it's that the deliverable itself has changed.

3
00:00:10,137 --> 00:00:14,350
Instead of text suggestions, you receive completed work.

4
00:00:14,350 --> 00:00:19,937
This shift is the foundation for understanding every feature we'll cover later in the course.

